<div class="container">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <h1 class="text-2xl text-center">Simple Wishlist</h2>
    <p>
    A web app to create the most basic version of a Wishlist (or any list of URLs that you'd like).
    </p>
    <p>
    Keep lists private to keep tabs on items that you're interested in. Or create shareable links
    to send your lists to friends &amp; family.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col mt-2">
      <%= link_to "Create an account", new_registration_path, class: "button-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Log in", new_session_path, class: "button-default" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div
